Developer Terms of Use
des: History happens every day! Check in with Alexa to find out about the historical events that happened on this day and every other day of the year. Come back each day and say 'Alexa, open Historical Day to hear the top historical event for the day. You can also ask Alexa for a historical event for any other day by saying “Alexa, ask Historical Day what happened on February 4th”, for example.
